September 13, 2024 - Silver Jeans Co. is a designer denim company founded in Winnipeg, Manitoba, Canada in 1991 by Michael Silver. Silver Jeans Co. also produces outerwear and T-shirts. Silver Jeans is manufactured by Western Glove Works, a family-owned company that has produced denim products since 1921.
